    <item>
      <title>南非新任部长支持医疗保险改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/south-africa-s-nhi-plan-new-minister-backs-health-insurance-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非新任卫生部长支持最近颁布的一项为全民健康保险奠定基础的法律，表明尽管失去了议会多数席位，他的政党仍有决心贯彻这项备受争议的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/south-africa-s-nhi-plan-new-minister-backs-health-insurance-revamp</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 11:41:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟 ESG 基金新规出台后，巴克莱面临 300 亿美元抛售风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/barclays-sees-30-billion-selloff-risk-amid-new-eu-esg-fund-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行分析师的研究显示，如果资产管理公司打算在新规下保留 ESG 标签，那么在欧洲提供 ESG 基金的基金管理公司可能需要出售近 300 亿美元的股票和债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/barclays-sees-30-billion-selloff-risk-amid-new-eu-esg-fund-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的中间派联盟愿景已开始动摇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/macron-s-vision-of-a-centrist-alliance-is-already-faltering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙试图通过提前举行议会选举来化解他所造成的政治危机，但这一努力遭到了强烈反对，凸显了这位法国总统的权威正在减弱，也凸显了内部的深刻分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/macron-s-vision-of-a-centrist-alliance-is-already-faltering</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:49:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>津巴布韦将扩大碳产业与其他国家进行贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/zimbabwe-to-widen-carbon-industry-to-trade-with-other-nations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦正加紧为联合国框架下的碳交易新时代做好准备，该框架允许各国之间以及企业之间买卖碳信用额，以帮助实现其气候目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/zimbabwe-to-widen-carbon-industry-to-trade-with-other-nations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:28:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国每年必须筹集 150 亿欧元以满足欧盟要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/france-must-find-15-billion-annually-to-meet-eu-fiscal-demands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，法国下一届政府每年将需要增加收入或节省 150 多亿欧元（162 亿美元）才能满足欧盟的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/france-must-find-15-billion-annually-to-meet-eu-fiscal-demands</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:01:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国政府准备削减开支以安抚市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/french-government-readies-spending-cuts-to-reassure-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管下一届政府存在政治不确定性，法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔仍继续推进计划中的支出削减措施，以向市场和欧盟保证法国的财政信誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/french-government-readies-spending-cuts-to-reassure-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
